article.description: Matt Lewis and Dwight Wilson scored 26 points apiece as James Madison narrowly beat Towson 74-73 in the first round of the Colonial Conference Tourney on Saturday.
article.headline: James Madison defeats Towson 74-73 in CAA tourney
article.linkText: James Madison defeats Towson 74-73 in CAA tourney
article.story: NORTH CHARLESTON, S.C. -- Matt Lewis and Dwight Wilson scored 26 points apiece as James Madison narrowly beat Towson 74-73 in the first round of the Colonial Conference Tourney on Saturday. Lewis shot 9 for 11 from the foul line. Wilson also had seven rebounds for the Dukes. Brian Fobbs had 18 points for the Tigers (10-22). Tobias Howard added 10 points.
